 Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780816642069\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780816642069\">9780816642069</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Hitchcock%27s+cryptonymies%3A+volume+1+secret+agents&amp;rft.place=Minneapolis&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Minnesota+Press&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.isbn=9780816642069&amp;rft.aulast=Cohen&amp;rft.aufirst=Tom&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATom+Cohen\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\">Cohen, Tom (2005). <i>Hitchcock's cryptonymies: volume 1 war machines</i>. Minneapolis: University of Minnesota Press. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780816641710\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780816641710\">9780816641710</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Hitchcock%27s+cryptonymies%3A+volume+1+war+machines&amp;rft.place=Minneapolis&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Minnesota+Press&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.isbn=9780816641710&amp;rft.aulast=Cohen&amp;rft.aufirst=Tom&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATom+Cohen\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite class=\"citation book\">Cohen, Tom; <a href=\"/wiki/Claire_Colebrook\" title=\"Claire Colebrook\">Colebrook, Claire</a>; <a href=\"/wiki/J._Hillis_Miller\" title=\"J. Hillis Miller\">Miller, J. Hillis</a> (2012). <i>Theory and the disappearing future: on De Man, on Benjamin</i>. Milton Park, Abingdon, Oxon New York: Routledge. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780415604536\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780415604536\">9780415604536